name: Ni WooCommerce Order Export
author: anzia

sections.description:
Ni WooCommerce Order Export Description

Sales order report and export
Sales order report shows all sales information in tabular or grid format like billing details, shipping details, order total and sales order product.

Order billing report and export
Order billing report display all billing details in tabular or grid format like billing name, email, contact number country and many more fields

Order shipping report and export
Order shipping report display all shipping details in tabular or grid format like shipping name, shipping address, shipping country and many more fields

Sales Summary report

  • Show top 10 recent order list on dashboard
  • Sales by order status in tabular format or pie chart
  • Sales by payment order in tabular format or pie chart
  • Export order details into csv format
  • Export billing details into csv format
  • Export shipping details into csv format
  • Search report

Report Filter option

  • Filter by date period (Today, yesterday, last 10 days, 30 day, 60 days)
  • Filter by order id
  • Filter by billing email address
  • Filter by billing first name
  • Filter by order status
  • Filter by country

Ni WooCommerce Order Export Setting
Ni WooCommerce Order Export provide the option to choose the report columns as per your requiremnt.

Export option

  • Export order report into CSV format
  • Print Sales order report

Ni WooCommerce Order Export Setting
Ni WooCommerce Order Export provides the option to choose the report columns as per your requirement.

Sales key indicators
WooCommerce Order Export provides the analytical dashboard that shows all key information to help you grow your online business.

  • Total Sales
  • This Year Sales
  • This Month Sales
  • This Week Sales
  • Yesterday Sales
  • Total Sales Count
  • This Year Sales Count
  • This Month Sales Count
  • This Week Sales Count
  • Yesterday Sales Count
  • Total Customer Count
  • Today Customer Count
  • Total Guest Customer Count
  • Today Guest Customer Count
  • Today Order Count
  • Today Sales
  • Today Product Sold
  • Today Discount
  • Today Tax

  • View Demo
  • Buy Now

Ni WooCommerce Order Export Pro version feature

  • Dashboard order summary
  • Sales Order report
  • Order Product Details report
  • Order Status wise sales report
  • Customer wise sales report
  • Payment Gateway wise sales report
  • Country wise sales report
  • Coupon wise sales report
  • Product wise sales report
  • Product Stock report
  • Filter all report with date range
  • CSV/Excel export

Support/Feedback Email/New Report Requirement

  • We are open to your suggestions and feedback – Thank you for using or trying out one of our plugins
  • support@naziinfotech.com

sections.installation:
1. Use the WordPress plugin installer or upload files to WordPress plugin directory.
  2. Activate “Ni WooCommerce Order Export” plugin from the admin panel.
  3. Find “Order Export” in the admin menu.
sections.faq:
Where i can get help?

Click on support tab or email: support@naziinfotech.com

Do you customize this plugin?

Yes, as per requirement we can customize this plugin.

Do you export more columns such as billing address, shipping address and other order details?

Yes, as per requirement we can add more columns.

Can you provide the filter based on customer name or email address?

Yes, we can add the filter on customer name, billing email and order number etc.
